name: Mixed-metal and Pyrite Earrings
description: These earrings are a nice combo of contemporary design and deco inspiration.  They're handmade by Los Angeles artist, Jivita Harris Casey.  Hanging from textured sterling silver "triangles" are 14k gold-fill wire wrapped pyrite beads.  These earrings measure 2 1/8" long, including the 14k gold-fill ear wires.

name: Brown Triangle Macrame Necklace
description: This is such a beautifully made necklace.  Designed by Ojai artist, Harper Belle, this necklace is made of oxidized sterling silver, pearls, and dainty  macrame.  The chain measures 17" long.

name: Pewter Kokino Stud Earrings
description: These unique earrings were made by F is For Frank.  The artist took Kokino flowers, made molds of them, and then caste them in pewter.  The posts on these earrings are sterling silver.  They measure 1/2" wide and 3/4" long.

name: Henna Earrings
description: These light-weight and versatile earrings were made by Portland designer Jennifer Goff of Paper Wings.  They're made of 14k gold-fill and oxidized sterling silver.  They measure 3 3/4" long, including the ear wires.

name: Pewter Kokino Flower Ring
description: This is a BIG ring, but it's adjustable so it fits everybody!  Handmade by F is For Frank, this ring was made my making a mold of a Kokino flower and casting it in pewter.  The flower measures 1 1/4" at its widest point.

name: Loop-d-loo Ring
description: This ring looks great on!  Made by Silver Lake designer, Azaara, it's made of a silver/copper alloy and plated with white gold and rhodium. All the cubic zirconia stones are hand set.  A fun ring to wear to a party... or every day!  It measures 1 3/4" long from loop to loop.  This ring is a size 7.

name: Crochet Sterling and Aqua Chalcedony Earrings
description: Such a fresh color, great looking with any skin tone! These earrings are handmade by Los Angeles designer, Arivka.  She takes sterling wire and skillfully hand crochets setting for the stones.  They measure 1 1/8" long, including the ear wires.

name: Gold-fill Crochet and Smokey Quartz Necklace
description: This is a perfect necklace!  Not too big, nor too small.  A gorgeous smokey quartz gemstone that's easy to wear with any color... etc. etc.  It's made by Los Angeles designer Arivka.  She hand crochets the settings from 14k gold-fill wire.  Because this stone is so translucent, you can see the wire work  through the stone which is such a pretty effect.  The stone with the setting measure a little over 3/4 " long.  The chain is 18" long, not including the 1" extension for extra length.

name: Gold-Plated Aqua Chalcedony Ring
description: This ring is made of hypo-allergenic base metal and plated in 18k gold.  The setting that holds the chalcedony gemstone measures 1/2" x 3/8".  This ring is a size 6.  Such a great gift at this price!

name: Sterling Crochet Gemstone Necklaces
description: These dainty little necklaces were made by Arivka, one of our best selling jewelry designers.  She takes sterling (or gold-fill) wire and hand crochets settings for the gemstones.  Featured here is a round moonstone, teardrop aqua chalcedony, and a teardrop labradorite.  The chains measure 17" long, not including a 1" extension for extra length.

name: Sterling Silver Gray Diamond and White Topaz Earrings
description: These elegant earrings are handmade in Philadelphia by Michelle Pressler. A perfect mix of contemporary design and vintage inspiration.  They're made of slightly oxidized sterling silver, gray diamond beads, and faceted white topaz gems.  They measure 1 1/3 inches long, including the ear wires.

name: Black Sterling Feather Necklace
description: This necklace is so cool!  A little rock-n-roll mixed with sexy sophistication.  Handmade of oxidized sterling silver by Seattle designer Paper Wings, this necklace is sure to be a go-to piece when ever you feel like showing the world what a badass you are! The chain is 17" long and the spikes measure 3 1/2" at their longest point.

name: Blue Topaz, Apatite, and Labradorite Earrings
description: The combination of color and gems on these earrings is fantastic!   They're made of sterling silver, blue topaz, apatite, and labradorite.  They measure 2 1/4" long, including the sterling silver ear wires.

name: Blue Topaz, Apatite, and Labradorite Necklace
description: This necklace has so much personality!  Made by Joli Jewelry in New York, it's made of blue topaz, apatite, labradorite, and various beads.  It has a leather cord and measures 16" long, not including the 2" gold-fill extension chain.

name: Sterling, Serpentine, and Pyrite Earrings
description: These elegant earrings were handmade in New York by Joli Jewelry.  Long green serpentine stones are topped with pyrite beads.  The measure a bit over 2" long, including the sterling silver ear wires.

name: Gold Plated Swirl Hoops
description: These earrings are practical like a classic hoop, but much more unique!  They very light weight and made of hypo-allergenic base metal and plated with 18k yellow gold. They measure 1 1/4" across.

name: Aloe Vera Cufflinks
description: We couldn't resist getting these cufflinks for the store.  The artist made molds of aloe vera and caste them in pewter.  A unique gift and a great addition to any cufflink collection. They measure 7/8" long.

name: Pewter California Cufflinks
description: For the man (or woman) whose got style and Cali pride.  Handmade of pewter.  If you know someone with a cufflink collection, we bet they don't have these!  They measure approximately 1' long.

name: Oxidized Sterling, Pearl, Pyrite, and Green Quartz Necklace
description: This love necklace was made by Philadelphia artist, Michelle Pressler.  It's made of oxidized sterling, freshwater pearl, pyrite, and green quartz to add a little color.  It measures a standard 16" long, not including a 1" extension.

name: Pearl, Pyrite, and Green Quartz Bracelet
description: This pretty and feminine bracelet was made by Philadelphia artist, Michelle Pressler.  It's made of oxidized sterling silver, freshwater pearls and pyrite.  It fits wrists 6 1/2 to 7 1/2 inches.

name: Brown Ceramic Trio
description: These vases are the perfect blend of organic and contemporary. Their miniature size makes it easy to find a place to display them. The tallest vase is 3 1/3 tall.  Made of porcelain and hand etched/glazed. You get all three vases for only $68!

name: Gold-Plated Lemon Quartz Studs
description: Pretty and classic square lemon quartz studs.  The base metal is hypo-allergenic and nickel free.  It's plated with 18k gold.  Settings measure a bit over 1/4" wide.

name: Retro Leather Card Case/Mini Wallet
description: These are so cool!  Each case is handmade in San Francisco using vegetable-dyed American Leather. They can be used for business card or as a mini wallet.  Choose from 3 designs.

name: Takin' Care of "Business"- Business Card and Condom Case Set
description: We love the pairing of these two items!  A great gift for the fun, yet responsible men (or women) in your life.  The set includes one business card case and one condom case.  They're handmade in Los Angeles. There are 4 sets to choose from.

name: Wall-mounted Bottle Openers
description: These wall-mounted bottle openers are handmade in San Francisco.  A great gift for someone with a man cave... or woman cave!  It comes with the hardware to easily mount it to wall or wood.  Choose from 3 designs.

name: Bronze and Pyrite Inlay Hoops
description: We've sold jewelry by hundreds of designers over the years, but only one does pieces like this!  Handmade in New York by David Urso, these hoops are works of art.  David took pyrite, crushed it, and then set it in bronze hoops.  The ear wires are sterling silver.  Though pyrite is a weighty stone, these hoops are nice and light. Their diameter is 1 3/4".

name: Big Fabulous Druzy Cuff
description: This cuff is so striking and sure to be a conversation piece.  It was designed by Los Angeles based Brazilian designer Marcia Moran.  It's made of a hypo-allergenic based metal and heavily plated with rhodium, which is a derivative of platinum.  On top is a beautiful titanium coated druzy stone.  It's 1 1/4' wide and is malleable, so it'll fit most wrists.

name: Mustard and Gray Slouch Bag
description: This beautiful bag is handmade in Finland by Carita Viola Designs (my mom).  It measures 15" wide and 10" deep.  It has an adjustable strap, a large zipper compartment inside, and an interior patch pocket.  Well made, vegan, and super stylish!

name: Purple Floral Clutch
description: This beautiful little clutch is handmade in Finland by Carita Viola Designs (my mom).  It measures 9 1/2 " long and has a wrist strap that can be tucked under the flap if you don't want to use it.

name: Turtles
description: The cutest little turtles ever!  These creatures are the result of a collaboration between architect Sindy Passo and Mayan artists in Mexico.  No two are alike!  They're made of 100% natural wool and measure approximately 5" from head to tail.

name: Gold Crochet and Cobalt Druzy Earrings
description: Dazzling, sparkly, and very special!  Los Angeles artist, Arivka hand crochets bezels to cradle these beautiful cobalt druzy earrings.  All the metal used is 14k gold-fill.  They measure 1 1/4" long, including the ear wires.

name: Hippos
description: Hippos are said to be dangerous and ferocious, but as you can see by these sweet faces, that just can't be true!  These creatures are the result of a collaboration between architect Sindy Passo and Mayan artists in Mexico.  No two are alike!  They're made of 100% natural wool and measure approximately 7" from head to tail.

name: Bronze Arc Hoops
description: We love these earrings!  Handmade in Los Angeles by Tiffany Kunz, these hoops are made of a lustrous yellow bronze with 14k gold-fill posts.    They measure 1 3/4" long and are almost 1 1/4 " wide.

name: Silver Bead And Thread Bracelet Set (4 choices)
description: Layering is in!  These sweet little bracelets are hand woven and threaded with silver colored beads.  One of the bracelets has evenly spaced flat beads and its mate has a a string of beads on the top.  The bracelets are adjustable, so one size fits all.  Choose from four fun color ways.

name: Gold Bead and Thread Bracelet Set (3choices)
description: Layering is in!  These sweet little bracelets are hand woven and threaded with brass beads.  One of the bracelets has evenly spaced flat beads and its mate has a a string of beads on the top.  The bracelets are adjustable, so one size fits all.  Choose from three fun color ways.

name: Sterling Silver Bohemian Charm Necklace
description: Romantic, feminine, and just plain cool!  Designed by Ojai, California artist Harper Belle, this necklace is made of oxidized sterling and is adorned with tiny peach pearls, labradorite, prehnite, and green amethyst gems.  The chain measure a bit over a standard 16".

name: Oxidized Sterling and Pyrite Earrings
description: These elegant earrings were made by San Francisco artist, Mashka.  They're made of oxidized sterling silver and pyrite gemstones.  A cool look for day or night!  They match perfectly with the Prong Necklace.  They measure 2 1/4" long.

name: Red and Blue Vintage Earrings
description: Adorable! The artist made these earrings by taking vintage enamel jewelry parts and adding bright red beads. The measure 1 1/2" long, including the 14k gold-fill ear wire.

name: Big Coral Colored Vintage Earrings
description: What a fabulous pair of earrings! The artist takes vintage components and makes them new again.  These lightweight earrings measure 2" long, including the sterling silver ear wire.

name: Gold-Plated Lemon Quartz Ring
description: A fun and sparkly ring at a great price!  It's made of hypo-allergenic base metal that's plated with 18k gold.  The setting measures approximately 3/8" wide.  It's a size

name: Gold-Plated Gemstone Stack Rings (sold separately)
description: Rings at this price make creating a stack set very affordable.  Of course they are great on their own too!  Each ring is made of a hypo-allergenic base metal and plated with 18k gold.  A perfect gift!  All the rings in this picture are a size 7. The settings of the round and triangular rings are a little wider than a 1/4", while the square setting is 3/8" wide.

name: Gold-Plated Gem Stack Rings (sold separately)
description: Rings at this price make creating a stack set very affordable.  Of course they are great on their own too!  Each ring is made of a hypo-allergenic base metal and plated with 18k gold.  A perfect gift!  All the rings in this picture are a size 6. The settings of the round rings are a little wider than a 1/4", while the square setting is 3/8" wide.

name: Amazonite and Pearl Necklace
description: This stunning and colorful necklace was made by Philadelphia artist, Michelle Pressler.  It's made of 14k gold-fill, amazonite (center), fresh water pearls, and blue cz stones.  The pendant is a little bit over 3/4" in length.  The chain is  17" long.

name: Amazonite and Pearl Earrings
description: What a color!  Handmade by Michelle Pressler, these earrings are made of 14k gold-fill, amazonite (center), fresh water pearls, and blue cz stones.  They measure 1 1/4" long including the ear wires.

name: Oxidized Sterling and Red Macrame Necklace
description: This bohemian treasure features a delicate red macrame pendant with oxidized sterling chain and beads as well as tiny pearls.  The chain measures 17" long.

name: Vintage Swirl Earrings
description: Such fun earrings!  Designer by Joli Jewelry in Brooklyn, these earrings combine vintage with new.  The main part of the earring is brass and is adorned with gems and crystals.  The ear wires are 14k gold-fill.  They measure 2 1/2" long, including the ear wire.

name: Oxidized Sterling and Gemstone Prong Necklace
description: You've never seen a necklace like this before!  An impressive statement piece made my Northern California artist, Mashka, it's made of oxidized sterling silver, pearls, labradorite, and pyrite.   Wear it with a t-shirt.  Wear it with a cocktail dress.  Wear it with everything!  The chain measures a standard 16" long, not including the 2" extension.  The longest center prong is 2" long.

name: Sterling and Pyrite Coin Earrings
description: These earrings are made by New York based designer, David Urso.  Using his patented technique, he takes pyrite gems, crushes them, and sets them in a light-weight resin.  Surrounding the pyrite is a rough textured sterling silver. The circles measure 3/4" in diameter. Perfect for the person who likes to make a statement with simple, yet contemporary jewelry.  The wearer should be prepared to receive attention, as David's work always inspires curiosity.

name: Gold Druzy Necklaces
description: These necklaces are made by one of our best-selling designers, Arivka.  She uses 14k gold-fill wire to hand crochet the settings to create distinctively unique and feminine pieces.  The 14k gold-fill chains measure 18" long, not including a 1" extension for extra length.  The small round pendant is  3/8" wide.  The medium teardrop pendant is approximately 7/8" long and 5/8" wide.

name: Oxidized Sterling and Lemon Quartz Earrings
description: What an amazing color!  These earrings are made of sparkly lemon quartz gemstones  and oxidized sterling silver.  They measure 1" long, including the ear wires.

name: Mixed-metal and Pearl Flower Cluster Necklace
description: This necklace is so striking and unique!  Handmade by Northern California artist, Mashka, it features oxidized sterling silver and white freshwater pearls.  Each pearl is fastened in 14k gold-fill to give a subtle contrast to the silver.  The chain measures a standard 16"long, and has a 2" extension for extra length.

name: Sterling Silver Floral Shield Ring
description:
This is a bold ring for every day wear!  It has a beautiful raised floral design on it and is oxidized to show of the intricate detail.  The domed shield  measures 1 1/2 inches wide.  It's a size 7.

The hand modeling the ring is smaller than average.

name: Big Labradorite Cocktail ring.
description:
We love labradorite and this ring definitely hits the spot!  It has a big emerald cut bluish green labradorite gemstone set in sterling silver.  The metal work has a hammered texture with a slightly matte finish. The setting measures almost 3/4" wide.  It's a size 7.

Note:  The glass hand is smaller than the average hand.

name: Big Lemon Citrine Cocktail Ring
description:
This ring is something to behold, especially in person!  It has a large beautifully cut grade A lemon citrine gemstone set in sterling silver.  the metal on the band has a hammered texture with a slightly matte finish. The setting measures 3/4" wide.  It's a size 7.  

Note: The glass hand is smaller than the average hand.

name: Cotton Tree Scarf
description: Who says a scarf can't have personality and still be versatile?  This high quality scarf has very generous dimensions,  44" wide and 78" long.  Because it made of a light 100% cotton fabric, it can be worn many different ways!

name: Cotton Wild Horses Scarf
description: Who says a scarf can't have personality and still be versatile?  This high quality scarf has very generous dimensions,  44" wide and 78" long.  Because it made of a light 100% cotton fabric, it can be worn many different ways!

name: Cotton Fish Scarf
description: Who says a scarf can't have personality and still be versatile?  This high quality scarf has very generous dimensions,  44" wide and 78" long.  Because it made of a light 100% cotton fabric, it can be worn many different ways!

name: Alameda Hoops
description: What a cool pair of earrings.  Practical like a classic hoop, but so much more interesting!  Handmade in Portland by Betsy and Iya, these earrings are made of bronze, brass, and 14k gold-fill.  The "bars" are hand caste bronze.  The curve is brass, and the ear wires are 14k gold-fill.  They measure almost 3" long.

name: Raw Black Diamond Circle Earrings
description: Raw diamonds are trendy at the moment, but when set in a classic setting, they'll be appreciated for years to come. A sterling silver circle shape contains a mosaic of raw black diamonds that catch the light beautifully.  They measure 1" long, including the ear wire.

name: Raw Black Diamond Teardrop Earrings
description: Raw diamonds are trendy at the moment, but when set in a classic setting, they'll be appreciated for years to come. A sterling silver teardrop shape contains a mosaic of raw black diamonds that catch the light beautifully.  They measure a bit over 1 1/4" long, including the ear wire.

name: Turquoise and Sterling Ring
description:
This one-of-a-kind ring boasts a big piece of organically shaped turquoise that's hard to take your eyes off of!  The stone is 1 3/4" long and is a little over 1" wide.  It's a size 7 1/2.

Note: The model has a smaller than average sized hand.

name: Azurite and Sterling Ring
description:
This one-of-a-kind ring is gorgeous!  It has a big azurite gemstone bezel set in sterling silver. The stone is 1 1/4" long and 7/8" wide.  The band is a size 7.

Note: The model has a smaller than average sized hand.

name: White Druzy and Sterling Ring
description:
This one-of-a-kind ring is a show stopper!  It has a large white druzy gem that measures 1 1/2 " long and 3/4" wide.  It's set in sterling silver and is a size 7.

Note: The model has a smaller than average hand, so it appears larger than it is.

name: Bronze Arc Ring
description: Love, love, love this ring!  It's made by Los Angeles based designer Tiffany Kunz and is beyond comfortable.  It's available in whole sizes in both sterling silver and bronze.

name: Astrology Necklace
description:
This is one of our best selling necklaces!  We love how subtle it is, as it's not immediately obvious that it's an astrological constellation. Los Angeles based artist, Carla De La Cruz, creates these pieces by hand setting tiny 14k gold-fill beads into a beautifully luminous navy enamel resin.  Each piece is bezeled in metal and stamped with the astrological name. (Gemini is shown in the picture)

These lovely necklace are available in sterling or 14k gold-fill.  If we don't have one in stock at the time of your order Carla will make one for you right away.  You'll have it within 1-2 weeks.

name: Dainty 14k Rose Gold-fill and Sterling Necklace
description:
This piece is one of our own and can be worn everyday!  It's made of very delicate 14k rose gold-fill chain and sterling beads. It measures 17" long.  Makes a great gift! 

Available three ways: rose gold-fill  chain with sterling beads (shown), yellow gold-fill chain with sterling beads, OR sterling chain with yellow gold-fill beads.

name: Sterling, Rainbow Moonstone, and Pearl Double Necklace
description: This is one of our own creations. This double necklace has two strands fastened with one clasp. It's made of sterling silver, tiny freshwater pearls, and a cabochon rainbow moonstone gem.  Get the layered look in one necklace!

name: Brown and Black Messenger Bag
description: Style meet practicality!  This messenger bag was handmade in Finland by Carita Viola Designs (Sumi's mom).  It features a zipper compartment on the flap as well as one on the inside to keep your wallet secure.  It has two pockets on the outside (under flap) that are great for keys and cell phones.  It has an adjustable strap to suit any wearer.  The body of the bag measures 12" wide and is 10 1/2" deep.  All Carita Viola bags are limited edition, so if you don't want to wear what everybody else is wearing, this bag is for you!

name: Gray Printed Messenger Bag
description: Style meet practicality!  This messenger bag was handmade in Finland by Carita Viola Designs (Sumi's mom). name: Gold Rose Cut Diamond Twig Ring
description: This is our best selling diamond ring!  Made by artist Just Jules, it's made of 14k gold and 4 rose cut diamonds (.15ct).  The ring we have in stock is a 6 1/2, but the artist can make one just for you any size!  Allow 2-4 weeks for special orders.  This ring can also be made in white gold for about $30 more.  If you prefer full cut diamonds, that's also an option (call for pricing).

name: Rectangular Diamond Ring
description: This one-of-a-kind vintage inspired ring by Just Jules is to die for!  It's made of 14k yellow gold with a .35 carat rose cut diamond in the center with a full cut pave diamond surround (.15ct). It's a size 6 3/4.

name: Carnelian Whisper Necklace
description: Sweet and feminine!  This necklace has a faceted carnelian gem that is strung and knotted on gray silk cord and finished off with a sterling clasp.  Our whisper necklaces measure 17", but can be made in other lengths.  Just ask!  Makes a great gift!

name: Cherry Quartz Whisper Necklace
description: Sweet and feminine!  The necklace has a faceted cherry quartz gem that is strung and knotted on gray silk cord and finished off with a sterling clasp.  Our whisper necklaces measure 17", but can be made in other lengths.  Just ask!  Makes a great gift!

name: Green Onyx Whisper Necklace
description: Sweet and feminine!  This necklace has a vibrant faceted green onyx gem on knotted silk cord and finished with a sterling clasp.  Our whisper necklaces measure approximately 17", but can be made at other lengths too.  Just ask!  A perfect gift!

name: Blue Topaz Whisper Necklace
description: Sweet and feminine! This sparkly faceted blue topaz gem is strung and knotted on a silk cord and finished off with a sterling clasp.  Our whisper necklaces measure approx. 17", but can be made at other lengths too.  Just ask!  A perfect gift.

name: Seafoam Hip Bag
description:
This bag is beyond convenient!  It can be worn around the waist, but can also be worn as a regular shoulder bag.  The strap is adjustable, fitting hips 32" to 50". It has a zippered compartment as well as two pockets under the flap.  The body of the bag is 8 1/4" wide and 7" tall.
Each bag is either one-of-a-kind or limited edition, so you're not likely to  see yours being worn by someone else!  Handmade in Finland by Carita Viola Designs.

Each bag is either one-of-a-kind or limited edition, so you're not likely to  see yours being worn by someone else!  Handmade in Finland by Carita Viola Designs.

name: Ruby Mix Earrings
description: These elaborate earrings by Mashka are really special.  They resemble a cluster of flowers with rubies, garnets, amethysts, pink topaz, and carnelian gems. The "cups" are 18k vermeil.  The rest of the metal is 14k gold-fill.  They measure 2 1/2 inches long.

name: Long Mixed Metal Chain Earrings
description: These light weight earrings go perfectly with our mixed metal cluster and slide necklaces.  The chain and ear wires are 14k gold-fill and the sparkly oval beads are sterling silver.  They measure about 3" long including the ear wires.

name: Mixed Metal Swing Earrings
description: These light weight earrings go perfectly with our mixed metal cluster and slide necklaces!  The ear wires and chain are 14k gold-fill, and the beads are both sterling silver and 18k vermeil.  The measure about 3" long including the ear wires.

name: Mixed Metal Slide Necklace
description: This easy-to-wear necklace has a 14k gold-fill chain and clasp, and sparkly faceted sterling oval beads that move freely.  A great piece to wear everyday and a terrific price for giving as a gift!

name: Mixed Metal Cluster Necklace
description: This easy to wear necklace has a 14k gold-fill chain and clasp, with sparkly faceted sterling beads that move freely on the chain.  A great piece for wearing everyday and a terrific price for giving as a gift.  The chain measures 17" long and is a part of our own exclusive line, so if you want it a little shorter or longer that's an option!

name: Frog Felting Kit
description: Have you seen a cuter frog?  What a great gift for your crafty friends! This kit includes all you need to make this wool felted frog, including step-by-step picture instructions.

name: Big Bronze Etched Earrings
description: Stunning!  These are the earrings you put on to make a statement!  Handmade in Los Angeles of etched bronze.  The ear wires are 14k gold-fill.  These earrings have some weight to them, but they're not overly heavy.

name: Long Bronze Etched Leaf Necklace
description: This is a great piece to wear layered or alone.  Handmade in Los Angeles, this necklace is made of vintage bronze chain and etched bronze "leaves".  It measures 34" long, and because it has a clasp, it can be worn doubled.

name: Custom Vintage Book Necklaces
description:
This is a terrific gift idea!  You can have one of these necklaces made with a name or even a favorite/significant word.  The artist takes your word and authors it into text that she creates.  She then prints the text on blank vintage book paper.  Choose from three metals: aged bronze (shown), gunmetal, or copper.  They can be made in either 24" or 30" if you want to wear it long.

Once you've placed the order, we will contact you to get the name or word you'd like to have in your necklace!  Allow 1-2 weeks for delivery.

name: Vintage Book California Necklace
description: We're very excited about these necklaces!  The artist cuts pieces out of vintage books, circles a key word, and sets it behind magnified glass.  The chain and setting are a bronze colored base metal. The chain is 24" long, but can easily be shortened.  If you'd like for us to shorten it, just let us know!

name: Black Scarf
description: This is such a fresh and fun scarf!  It can be worn a variety of ways, even as a head wrap.  It's made of cotton and trimmed with soft lace.  Nice and light so that it can be worn year-round.

name: Teal Scarf
description:

Note:  This scarf shows blue in the photos, but it is a teal color.

name: Melting Glass T-light
description: These are so cool!  Found this glass artist on my yearly trip to Tallinn, Estonia. ( It's only an hour and half by boat from where my family lives in Helsinki.)
